{"tid":1540303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭撤回收例 各區市民唔收貨","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:50:35.000Z","uid":175808,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"75c7ae3f0a800149f1bf3f80590a536ae21a9dd1","tid":1540303,"uid":175808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"大家想聽日報紙headline 靜係講撤回收例?<br />\n定係想見到多句市民其實唔收貨?<br />\n如果係後者今晚就要踴躍d 表達意見喇<br />\n唔收貨呢個message 唔係今日講爭好遠㗎<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"18ee159557737210eac91b69f52f3d69260e6509","tid":1540303,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 應承我！<br />\n一日未答應五大訴求 都要繼續上街</span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1018bb76b2e783db5865a0e29e73ede19b40837a","tid":1540303,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"又話唔可以撤回？<br />\n你叫班藍絲同黑警支持左你咁耐令到自己神憎鬼厭係為左咩野？<br />\n原來有暴徒先會聽市民講野<br />\n但我唔想每一次都要抗爭政府先會聽我講野<br />\n所以寫左係基本法既雙普選係一定要有！<br />\n若果之前話唔可以撤回呢家又變可以既話<br />\n咁即係其餘四大訴求都應該可以由做唔到變做到!<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"ac7baa095a6d76e90c5e94355c77f3520b43719f","tid":1540303,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/hk908ch/11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk908ch%2F11&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbhURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=957ae239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk908ch/11</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美領行動投票Channel"},{"pid":"4cad42f67f5e76b530700f350cfddf59894fec2f","tid":1540303,"uid":175808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"1/10<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e1993461cb7fa29c6c95d60c8f28949558ccbacf","tid":1540303,"uid":78651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:20:02.000Z","msg":"第六訴求:取消單程証！"},{"pid":"c18f876773efa5d5ba33a221187425a9f462b80b","tid":1540303,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:20:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"553b66c014df65f291eade17588cf83cf2cf8038","tid":1540303,"uid":175808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n<br />\n大家要諗下去邊度表達意見最effective 呀<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"2c126434a2aa45c6557ffd717d99775862ed45d7","tid":1540303,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdcLSU.jpg&h=7d8fce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://